# Task 1: Project Setup

## Goal
Set up the project structure and dependencies

## Scope
- Create the project directory structure
- Install required NuGet packages
- Configure the database connection

## Technical Context
-.NET 8
- PostgreSQL
- xUnit
- JWT authentication

## Expected Files or Areas
- source/App.Api
- source/App.Services
- source/App.Data
- appsettings.json

## Technical Tasks
- Create the project directory structure
- Install required NuGet packages
- Configure the database connection
- Create the initial database migration

## Acceptance Criteria
- The project directory structure is set up correctly
- The required NuGet packages are installed
- The database connection is configured correctly
- The initial database migration is created